flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> RegistrationForm[User Fills Registration Form]
    RegistrationForm --> EnterPhone[Provide Phone Number]
    EnterPhone --> SendOTP[Call POST /api/auth/send-otp]
    SendOTP --> TwilioService[Twilio Sends SMS OTP]
    TwilioService --> EnterCode[User Enters OTP Code]
    EnterCode --> VerifyOTP[Call POST /api/auth/verify-otp]
    VerifyOTP --> CheckOTP{Is OTP Code Valid?}
    
    CheckOTP -- No --> RetryOTP[Show OTP Error, Allow Re-entry]
    RetryOTP --> EnterCode
    
    CheckOTP -- Yes --> UploadNIC[Upload NIC Front & Back Images]
    UploadNIC --> SubmitRegistration[Submit Registration Request]
    SubmitRegistration --> CheckFields{Are Required Fields Present?}
    
    CheckFields -- No --> BadRequest[Return 400 Bad Request]
    BadRequest --> SubmitRegistration
    
    CheckFields -- Yes --> HashPassword[Hash Password using bcrypt with salt = 12]
    HashPassword --> SaveFiles[Save uploaded images to uploads/nic/]
    SaveFiles --> InsertDB[Insert User into DB with status = pending]
    InsertDB --> SendWelcome[Send Welcome System Notification]
    SendWelcome --> End([End - Awaiting Admin KYC Verification])
